{"tid":1514803,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好一窩蜂寫信自薦做陪審員","createTime":"2019-08-29T01:46:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:48.000Z","uid":112636,"like":23,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"aaffe5c36b10e08ed4a7c3f61547af41cacca518","tid":1514803,"uid":112636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:46:43.000Z","msg":"記得我講過陪審員既問題嘛？我講過如果<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">案件唔上高院係無陪審員既</span></span></strong>。你認為DOJ會推幾百單案上高院？依家高院索償上限由一百萬提升到三百萬，佢地已經將好多案掉返落區域法院啦，你估高院好多人審案？<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">有人叫你地寫信自薦做陪審員，你地就一窩蜂去做，咁係咪話俾政府聽，你係 protestors sympathizers，同情抗爭者，叫政府閘你地名同記錄資料在案呀</span></span></strong>？明人不做暗事唔等如你唔需要保護自己，你對住既係一班無法無天既契弟，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你實名聯署同公開自薦，係咪自殺？</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我講呢D說話就係掃興架啦，you are free to label me as 熱狗或者熱普城，甚至乎係藍絲。我希望我估錯啦。<br />\n<br />\n陪審員否決權<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/skeptical.legal.fatman/posts/2387268598217445\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fskeptical.legal.fatman%2Fposts%2F2387268598217445&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=cf397d61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/skeptical.legal.fatman/posts/2387268598217445</a><br />\n<br />\n#上下社區法網就變法律精英的話<br />\n#我咪好很冤枉咁花左咁多學費同光陰<br />\n<br />\nsource：是咁的法網肥人<br />\n原post：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/skeptical.legal.fatman/posts/2407682786176026\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fskeptical.legal.fatman%2Fposts%2F2407682786176026&d=BKn7HUA2FwSq4MnMa2nFTHfp3ZHOIdf2SFoQnphXrww%3D&h=93ebd66d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/skeptical.legal.fatman/posts/2407682786176026</a>"},{"pid":"5ef471194b5ced32fbbfc562a8fe3464d71bd5a3","tid":1514803,"uid":40470,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:48:42.000Z","msg":"溫提：IVE仔唔好攞架來掉<br />\n<br />\n因為從公開試已知你無足夠語文能力，智力亦較低"},{"pid":"26704699aae29997c4d151fa05eecd21d9a00b08","tid":1514803,"uid":126590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T01:55:07.000Z","msg":"話做就做咩....陪審員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46c83efc5e83b604445db92735cf0c855608f889","tid":1514803,"uid":281342,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:01:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xnajp8B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXnajp8B.jpg&h=bc6d7b84&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ERTkT1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FERTkT1X.jpg&h=ba8cc5a1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gT3AHVi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgT3AHVi.jpg&h=426d2a35&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XsbeYtE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXsbeYtE.jpg&h=2a0b4a06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qMkjp8E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqMkjp8E.jpg&h=31193a5f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2372cf58c464cc1d7b4878d19b2140f40ae9fc16","tid":1514803,"uid":243380,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:09:55.000Z","msg":"咪帶風向啦傻仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6d082fe0ddb3603c21b811a804e26bba5defcf4","tid":1514803,"uid":271434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"楊衛隆：美國嘅香港民主法被泛民拖到十一月才能立法，將會有十萬手足被捕！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1513863\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1513863</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"45b5e75fd091b16276ee5bf8ef8c986d69e01559","tid":1514803,"uid":127929,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:32:11.000Z","msg":"on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"360d2777866609a1c43d31dfbe70f7b9c326979d","tid":1514803,"uid":216888,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:48:58.000Z","msg":"你都on9 唔比藍絲想做黎整死義士咩"},{"pid":"8dd840b131cc812e504b8be28f8e55237a6db673","tid":1514803,"uid":216888,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T02:49:52.000Z","msg":"我係藍絲既話都會想做陪審員 用下個死人腦先啦"},{"pid":"1e3ef3d17770282c39deb8e544972dd4e18c5015","tid":1514803,"uid":242497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:08:28.000Z","msg":"而家藍絲做陪審員都唔L得咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b63d0c2c61d45a091a4b0958bc03b3d91410c864","tid":1514803,"uid":205462,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T03:24:52.000Z","msg":"Common law之下， juror都係random咁選，除非有合理嘅原因 (例如Defendant係非洲裔，選出嘅陪審團全部係高加索裔人，可能對D造成偏見, 但都會係從收窄咗嘅pool隨機選人)，個pool如果夠大，randomly揀八至十個人做陪審團，唔係難事吧? <br />\n<br />\n就算可以自薦 (真係第一次聽到)，法官甚至雙方律師都可以提出反對自薦者作為陪審員之一<br />\n<br />\n當年我在海外被選中做juror，我係以要做clinical placement呢個原因, exempted唔需要做juror<br />\n<br />\nHigh Court唔止淨係得高額索償嘅civil cases, 仲有嚴重嘅criminal cases, 好似西九戲曲中心嘅串謀詐騙案咁 (分判商偷龍轉鳳，偷工減料)<br />\n<br />\n而且，自薦者會唔會可以淨係做佢想做嘅cases嘅jurors? 真係好有疑問，因為聽落已經係非常unjust同unfair, 唔相信有正常嘅法官會接納"},{"pid":"25ea44efa7912650e418afbcf71da64bf10cd4e4","tid":1514803,"uid":73945,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:08:56.000Z","msg":"5至10樓堆回覆做咩事<br />\n明明樓主講得啱<br />\n邊有可能自薦做陪審團<br />\n制度上唔可行之餘<br />\n仲會伸個頭出黎叫人快d DQ我"},{"pid":"a177b747c9affbd40a74eb348007f174f1ab7742","tid":1514803,"uid":101092,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T04:13:04.000Z","msg":"on lun 9"},{"pid":"010806bb34e402eb4ba7b5bfdc3d59bb81a242d1","tid":1514803,"uid":165782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:46:48.000Z","msg":"我就唔使驚 佢前幾日自動寄信叫我填<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]